snippet.title: Atoll New Map Full Gameplay (Day) #WEB3WAR v2.3 Winter Update | FPS | #Web3Gaming
snippet.description:
Exclusive gameplay from the new map Atoll as part of the Web3War v2.3 Winter update! The new update brings new maps and skins to the free-to-play first-person shooter game.

Web3War is a free-to-play competitive FPS available on Windows. Battle for supremacy, buy & sell insane NFT skins and prove your skill! Built by Roll1ng Thund3rz and secured by the Zilliqa blockchain. Download now at https://www.w3w.game/

Limited Edition NFT skins available now to buy & sell on the FUS1ON MARK3T and use in #WEB3WAR! Get it now at https://mark3t.store

The MARK3T is an easy-to-use platform for purchasing, managing, and trading cosmetic skin NFTs, tokens, and other digital assets linked to the Web3-enabled games available through the FUS1ON Gaming Hub.

Follow our socials for giveaways, teasers and more: https://news.w3w.game/m/web3war

Footage from the co-founder, Valentin aka the Sh3r1ff: https://twitter.com/ValentinCobelea

#W3W #WEB3GAMING #Zilliqa #fps #fpsskins #skins #web3 #nft #nftgaming #gaming
